  "A data analyst needs cos(θ/2) for a rotation transform, given that cos θ = 7/25 and θ is in Quadrant I. Using the half-angle formula, what is cos(θ/2)?": "",
  "√(16/25)": "",
  "7/50": "",
  "cos(θ/2) = √((1 + cos θ)/2) = √((1 + 7/25)/2) = √((32/25)/2) = √(32/50) = √(16/25) = 4/5. Positive because θ/2 is in Quadrant I.": "",
  "A physics teacher asks students to verify that cot²x + 1 = csc²x by starting from the Pythagorean identity. Which step correctly begins the verification?": "",
  "Divide sin²x + cos²x = 1 by cos²x": "",
  "Divide sin²x + cos²x = 1 by sin²x": "",
  "Multiply sin²x + cos²x = 1 by sin²x": "",
